node.text:
Brunches are great options for a first date. It is definitely a less formal alternative to the traditional dinner date and a lovely way to start the day! If you are meeting someone new, then the Sunday Brunch at The Raviz Kovalam is where you ought to head to.

For bookings contact: +91 471 305 1234 | 1800 4252 2220
mail: reservations.kovalam@theraviz.com | reservations@theraviz.com
